Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the start of Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:06.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather\nall the shards of the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:08.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new battle is beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:14.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I'm going to return\nto my present world and study hard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I intended,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but what awaited me was a battle\nmore frightening{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:18.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}than fighting the demons of\nthe Feudal Era!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to us and Miroku,\NSango, Shippo and Kirara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:22.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Travel back in time\nfor a Feudal Fairy Tale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:24.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all right for me to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:08.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure, there's nothing for\nyou to do here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis!\NWelcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nice to be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were gone for\nsome time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was hard coming up with\nexcuses for your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm glad you came back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NTired?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}really....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are.\NA present.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They told me it's a kind of\nrare dried food or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:15.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't wait to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be resting in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't ever leave you again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the type who'd go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:36.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when you do go,\NI'll be upset.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's to be expected, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'm getting weary\nof all this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, aren't you eating too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be going to school tomorrow\nafter a long absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need to store up energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I'll be able to stay here\nfor a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I'm going to switch gears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:20.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and study hard to catch up\nin all my classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's raring to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:24.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seconds, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:31.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:38.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll get a good night's sleep and forget\nall about the Feudal Era for a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:43.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm back to what I am...\na junior high school student.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:04:59.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:00.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're well enough to\nreturn to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:04.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:07.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were absent a long time\nthis time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A rare illness that made your ears\ncause hallucinations?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind me,\nwhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's been absent for\nsuch a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:25.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:26.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Preparations for the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:36.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cultural festival?\NBut what about classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Classes? We're too busy\nwith all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We just have classes\nin the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:46.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I have to come back\nwhen classes aren't crucial?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no sense in my being\nhere or there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you so depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:03.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shake it off, Kagome.\NC'mon, let's cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, let's sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it's energizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:12.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right! Kagome, you can participate\nin the festival, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:13.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right!\NWe sure need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A reserve?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:27.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, like a stand-in or substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right? Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine then. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, what do you want\nme to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sing in the choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Present the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perform on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:46.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As the heroine's friend,\NBrilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brilliant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now which do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- All of them!\N- Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:57.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Because you're our reserve.\N- And I want you to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've gone through a lot of practice\nand preparation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you'll be done with all this\nin a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Three duties should be easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, sing louder.\NFrom the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:33.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to create\nsomething unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm good at outdoor cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like a barbecue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grilling river fish over\na wood fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or grilling fern roots\nover a wood fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't say anything. Just keep\nyour hands moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:48.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, we'll start with\NBrilliant's line in Act 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:56.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ever since my grandfather collapsed\nfrom lumbago, I've {\i1}been....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Outstretch your arms\nand be more {\i1}appealing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:08.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My grandfather collapsed\nfrom {\i1}lumbago....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How does it taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:15.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not bad, if I do say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I wanna taste, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:17.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to all\nthat energy you gathered up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I used it all up in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were your studies that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even studying would've\nbeen better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:42.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The dried food you brought\nback is perfect with {\i1}sake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's tried to use\NKagome's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. To use her to\nfind the Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means Naraku doesn't know\nthe whereabouts
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,of all the Jewel shards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:08.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. And the fact that he went through\nthe trouble of kidnapping Kagome,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:12.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,must signify that there are shards which\NNaraku himself cannot find alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like which shards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:17.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably the ones\nin hard-to-find locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that means he's having\na hard time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:41.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you've come, Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard you coming\nfrom four leagues away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? Then that will\nmake this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:58.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mimisenri, they say that you possess\nears that are able to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,all things in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:04.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are right, Naraku. And I have\nheard rumors about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:08.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you intend to take my ears\nand make them part of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your filthy body doesn't\ninterest me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:18.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then why have you come\nall the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you heard of the\nwhereabouts of the Sacred Jewel shards?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:25.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} According to the demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, you possess nearly\nall of the shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just one. I need just\none more shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:38.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But its whereabouts has\neluded even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:39.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let me use my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:53.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All our shards are now\nin Naraku's possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Other than those, Koga has\ntwo in his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there's one which\nkeeps Kohaku alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:05.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:10.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Naraku succeeds in\ncompleting the Sacred Jewel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku will die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We won't let Naraku succeed, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:19.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:23.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll find the remaining shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, that's what I intend\nto do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:27.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know there's no need\nto remind {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you must be more\ndiligent about Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that she never falls\ninto Naraku's hands again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:43.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you eating there\nall by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:44.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:48.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The villagers and mountain priests\nwe saved recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They gave it to me in gratitude.\NSome of their dried food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:51.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We Demon Slayers keep warning them\nnot to do it, but it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Kirara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a hypha of a fungal\ndemon called Shironyudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But they're safe to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if you put it in water\nand heat {\i1}it....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meaning, if you boil it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A new Shironyudo is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that what that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:22.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I prefer that they be\nthrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was so tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why they're such a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget about the dried food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:35.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, finding the Sacred Jewel\nshard will solve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, that was the start\nof it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wherever Naraku is hiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:46.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he's sure to appear where\nthe Sacred Jewel shard is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, next pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:02.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ayumi.\NI caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all right. It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kagome!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll sing her alto solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:17.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! What solo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hand me that tape, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:24.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:28.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maki, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take her to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:40.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- How is she?\N- She has a sprained ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She won't be able to\nmove around for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Brilliant....{\i0}\N- Huh? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:51.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From this moment, you are\nno longer Brilliant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but Escargot Pudding,\nthe female lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:59.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now let's continue with rehearsals!\NEscargot, get on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:00.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that terrible of\nboth of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:08.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't being a reserve!\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no good. There aren't\nany good recipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there something that\npacks a {\i1}punch....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:20.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something with impact?\NThat no one has tasted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Nope.\N- Then can you find one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?\N{\i1}I....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:28.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have individual practice\nfor the choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Then I have stage rehearsals.\N- I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:37.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't count on me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've really recovered, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hojo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hear you've taken on\na lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not "taken on"!\NForced to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At first, it was just\nhelping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then it got more and {\i1}more....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You haven't been back\nin a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so everyone wants to give you\na big role in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Think so?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Hojo, do you know\nany unusual dishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not really into {\i1}cooking....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess I have to depend\non Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Oh!\N- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that you're playing\nthe heroine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we'll have quite a lot\nof scenes together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So how about we practice\ntogether?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:31.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:35.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:56.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, Escargot Pudding, will\nneither run nor hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:57.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something that packs a punch\nand has {\i1}impact....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,yet is not familiar to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, we need to start looking\nfor the Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got that right. Kagome takes her\nsweet time when we leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Inuyasha, ask Kagome for\nmore ninja food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:37.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These dried foods are tasty,\nbut a bit tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe I can boil it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:48.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? A {\i1}festival....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} The economy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:29.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that was the Shironyudo\NSango mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:42.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rest of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rest of the dried food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, the one in the pot is\nthe last of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I ate the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, did you come\nto have some fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not here for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you'll have dinner with\nus, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:02.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:13.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! We're goin' back\nafter we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You never said anything about\nmy returning early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! You know we can't\nfind the shards without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:26.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:29.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Whaddya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like my old self again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I felt like seeing {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:45.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:46.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:49.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boy, you're selfish, Inuyasha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't go back\njust yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not another one of\nthose "tests"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:57.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No. A cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cultural festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Singing in the choir, cooking,\nperforming on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can family members come\nto watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then we'll all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:17.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! I must see\nmy granddaughter perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Hey, can I go?\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because! Imagine the uproar if\npeople find out about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:25.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:32.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a lot to do, so I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's get ready, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:40.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd better dress up for this.\NOh yes, my {\i1}suit....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:49.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha and Kagome are\ntaking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gee, it's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It smells so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:02.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:10.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon in an area\npopulated by humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was a reconstituted demon\nof a Kurotengudake fungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:23.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon fungi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:31.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're going to get rid of all\nthe dried food we received.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You still had them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:37.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez....{\i0} They're so tasty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:46.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shironyudo, Kurotengudake,\NYumenamazu, Waraiazami,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:50.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hamadaruma, Kamitsuki-suika,\nand the {\i1}Esedaikoku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:53.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You had so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome took the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kagome?\N- Back home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:05.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Inuyasha is with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right. It'll be fine since\NInuyasha is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:12.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I heard that Inuyasha can't\nreally do as he pleases
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when he's in Kagome's country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:30.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Scuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:39.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's put the baked goods\nout on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:46.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On the day of the Cultural Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:48.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Home Economy classroom\nis in a shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.06,0:23:51.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Darn it.\NThat's the demon Kurotengudake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:53.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons terrorize the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:54.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where did they come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll exterminate them with\NHigurashi Shrine sutras!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:59.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you have an important\npresentation to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.74,0:24:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm scared, but I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:04.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it!\NPrepare to die, demons!
